resources.string:
Pay a fine imposed by the subdivisions of the State Automobile Inspectorate of the Ministry of Internal Affairs, it is possible in the bank cash desk, ATM, payment terminal, information kiosk, Internet banking, mobile banking. 

To pay a penalty in the "Calculation" system (ERIP), you must select: 
1) Ministry of Internal Affairs -> Penalties -> SAI -> Photo speed fixation (service no. 381141); 
2) enter the registration number of the offense (11 digits):%1$s; 
3) check the data on the offense (the surname, name, patronymic of the owner of the vehicle and the amount of the penalty); 
4) make a payment. 

After payment of the fine, information about its repayment is received within 2-3 minutes in the information systems of the Ministry of Internal Affairs, with a note on the execution of the penalty being automatically placed in the electronic violation card. 

Dimensions of penalties for violations detected by speed sensors: 
- for 10-20 km/h - 0.5 of the base value; 
- 20-30 km/h - 2 base values; 
- 30-40 km/h - 4 base units; 
- more than 40 km/h - 6 base units.
